name: Koala
text: Must have been quite the lengthy road you had.

name: Koala
text: Had quite the time to figure out a couple of jokes.

name: Koala
text: There was one in my mind that really stuck out.

name: Koala
text: It's hard to fight with diarrhea.

name: Koala
text: Fight your fears one step at a time.

name: Koala
text: I know a whole lot of tumbleweed passed as I said those.

name: Koala
text: But don't I ever feel more relived finally getting them out of my chest!

name: Koala
text: Good luck on your adventures traveler!
